  "body": "The plan is to move on to BLS12-381 signatures where the size of public key on the new curve are 48 bytes.\r\n\r\nCurrently VRC (validator registration contract) takes type `bytes32` for public key. Using BLS12-381, public key needs to be 48 bytes, I propose we change public key's type to `bytes` and check if it's 48 bytes or revert.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/master/contracts/validator-registration-contract/validator_registration.sol#L5",
